@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_khkhub(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.01)) * 0.73)
    v2 = (0.49 * (tmp - (v2 + 0.18 / tmp + 0.85)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.21 * 0.93))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin(0.04))
    v0 = wp.exp(0.30)
    tmp = (0.37 * wp.abs((v2 + 0.39 - v1 + 0.89)))
    tmp = v0
    v1 = (tmp / tmp)
    data[tid] = v0
